## Quarto

In Quarto enables you to weave together content and executable code into a finished document. To learn more about see [Quarto](https://quarto.org)

## Descriptive Statistics - Air Quality

@fig-airquality explores the impact of temperature on ozone[^1] level...

[^1]: Ozone is a molecule composed of three oxygen atoms.


::: {.cell hash='2023_MSC_DataAnalytics_Quarto_Demo_cache/html/fig-airquality_b268c1a42d9049029d3e6b680da761a1'}

```{.r .cell-code}
ggplot(airquality, aes(Temp, Ozone)) + 
  geom_point() + 
  geom_smooth(method = "loess")
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![Temperature and ozone level.](2023_MSC_DataAnalytics_Quarto_Demo_files/figure-html/fig-airquality-1.png){#fig-airquality}
:::
:::
